deck: Psychiatrist of Robyn Hood.
description:
Origin

George grew up with punk rock and a brother in a motorcycle gang.

Major Story Arcs

Robyn Hood: Riot Girls

His first session with Robyn Hood is interrupted by a demon. Robyn quickly disposes of the demon. George is left with the body in his office. Scared at first, he is actually reassured by Robyn's confidence.

Robyn Hood: Attitude Adjustment

Robyn believes it to be the last day on Earth and visits George for the last time. During their session, George is shot through the neck by Cabal member Red Death. He bleeds to death in his office.

deck: Geomancer from the year 4001 A.D. She is freed from captivity at the hands of Father by Rai's companions Lula Lee & Grace. They name her after a girl from a television series who is accidentally left behind by her family on an island - Karana.
description: Karana was held captive in New Japan by it's A.I. ruler, Father. The Eternal Warrior, tasked as the geomancer's protector, was unable to reach New Japan to free her. After Rai and his companions declare war on Father and begin fighting for the liberation of New Japan, she is freed from her prison by Lula Lee and Grace (Lula's positronic companion). Grace watches over her in Lula's hideout until Father's self defense protocol, unknowingly activated by Spylocke and Lula, begins to tear the floating city apart. As they flee Grace is crushed by falling debris and convinces Karana to climb in the escape pod alone.
name: Karana

deck: Francois Borillon is the Director of EuroMind, European Division of the S.H.I.E.L.D.
description:
History

Marvel Italia

Born in France, now in his early fifties, before becoming the Director of Euromind, Francois Borillon was a militar on O.N.U., member of the Blue Beret as Chief Commander, operating in many warzone such as Ex-Jugoslavia and other conflict of the Eastern Europe.

During that wars, his role was essential in the mediation between conflicting factions, and as Director of Euromind he have used his experience for manage the problem between the different division, usually negative towards military istitution. Being both a Militar and a Diplomat, Francois Borillon was always the right man to guide the Euroforce, answering only to Supreme Headquarters Allied Power Europe (S.H.A.P.E.)

Director Borillon was the coordinator and leader of both Task Force and Eurolab when, investigating a U.F.O. crash site in Malaysia, Task Force discovered mutated corpses wearing the insigna of the french multinational Nadir Inc., and was attacked by three Japanese super-armored cyborg mercenaries called Lords of War, working for A.I.M..

When the Eurolab, now changed in Euroforce, try to investigate the about the attack in Malaysia and save Iceboy [taken prisoner], the S.H.A.P.E. declare them criminals, ordering to Borillon to sop any comunication with the team and send Euromind soldier to capture them. S.H.A.P.E. show numberous video of Euroforce members killing Euromind Agents, but Borillion dosen't trust them, and after personal investigation, aid the Euroforce to avoid capture, faking their dead in the eyes of S.H.A.P.E. and giving them secret shelter and new documents.

After that Francois Borillon remain Director of Euromind, faking his trust in S.H.A.P.E. while secretly working for prove their corruption and aid the Euroforce.

All-New Marvel Now

Francois Borillon dosen't appear within the second line-up of Euroforce. Her current whereabout is unknown.

Powers

Director Borillon have no real power, but he is an expert militar and have very high Diplomatic and charismatic skills and a great intellect. For any purpouse he can use all the Euromind resource, gadget and agents.

As Director of Euromind he must be classified as Level 9 in the S.H.I.E.L.D. ranking.

deck: Owner of Cup O'Joe on King Street.
description:
Origin

When her mother died, Kayla was forced to take care of her little brother Billy and provide for them both. She started a shop called Cup O'Joe on King Street, next to an abandonned bakery. Some time later, in that bakery, the Gingerdead Man was resurrected.

After hearing screams from the bakery, she sent for some cops. The unprepared cops were killed by the Gingerdead Man. Kayla then took it upon herself to destroy the Gingerdead Man and his army of Mini-Gingers. She stopped the Gingerdead Man by throwing him into a cup of hot coffee, which dissolved him.
name: Kayla Martinez
